@node towupper
@section @code{towupper}---translate wide characters to uppercase
@findex towupper
@strong{Synopsis}
@example
#include <wctype.h>
wint_t towupper(wint_t @var{c});

@end example
@strong{Description}@*
@code{towupper} is a function which converts lowercase wide characters to
uppercase, leaving all other characters unchanged.

@*
@strong{Returns}@*
@code{towupper} returns the uppercase equivalent of @var{c} when it is a
lowercase wide character, otherwise, it returns the input character.

@*
@strong{Portability}@*
@code{towupper} is C99.

No supporting OS subroutines are required.

@*
